---
title: Turkey Fingers with Spicy Summer Slaw and Roasted Sweet Potato
description: Smoke Show hot sauce and mayo makes the perfect sauce for dipping. The smokey, sweet and spicy notes pair perfectly with the crisp sweet potato fries! This colourful meal is bright and oh so tasty.
